## Simulating your expenditure

\scriptsize

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
simulate_expenditure <- function() {
  costs <- rnorm(1, mean = 2000, sd = 500)
  if (runif(1) < 0.10) {
    costs <- costs + 1000
  }
  return(costs)
}
```
:::



