## Simulating your savings over 12 months

\scriptsize

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
simulate_monthly_savings <- function() {
  return(simulate_income() - simulate_expenditure())
}
simulate_yearly_savings <- function() {
  return(cumsum(replicate(12, simulate_monthly_savings())))
}
```
:::


